<#tt0058458-jdeferrari>
	schema:about <#tt0058458>;
	schema:author "jdeferrari";
	schema:dateCreated "Wed Dec 17 2003 00:00:00 GMT+0100 (Mitteleurop√§ische Normalzeit)";
	schema:reviewRating 8;
	schema:headline " Sure and unflinching";
	schema:reviewBody "Truffaut's study of a middleaged man losing his way in life in the ageold fashion is caught in a mesmerizing series of quicksuccession shots and sympatheticallycaptured quotidian details. An unthinking selfassured man his wounded passionate wife his sweet vulnerable lover an inevitable tragedy. This underrated film has no real surprises but its surefootedness is impressive and the simple story ultimately very moving.".

