<#tt0058458-erica_14>
	schema:about <#tt0058458>;
	schema:author "erica_14";
	schema:dateCreated "Wed Aug 11 1999 00:00:00 GMT+0200 (Mitteleurop√§ische Sommerzeit)";
	schema:headline " portrait of a weak man";
	schema:reviewBody "This is not one of the best Truffaut but it is nevertheless a precise portrait of a little man passive without courage and unable to really choose he will pay for that. Best sides of the movie the rapid sketch of a small town's wealthy people trying to be acculturate and Francoise Dorleac really charming as the protagonist's young lover".

